lyrics:
[Verse]
Maelys and her brother, they're always at odds
Bickering and fighting like two peas in a pod
But deep down they know they should spend more time
Playing together, making memories prime

[Chorus]
Let's settle the fights, make peace, and have some fun
Maelys and her brother, better as a team, not just one
Play together, laugh and sing, make your bond stronger
And don't forget to succeed in school, strive a little longer
